    "description": "<p>Estalished in 1998 and based in Singapore, AGI Freight Singapore Pte Ltd has grown from a fourman start up to a robust team with 25 staff strength. Today AGI is a successful ad profitable multi-modal service provider with internationally linked partners accross America, Europe and Asia Pacific. With over 10 years in operations, we have developed extensive networks across the globe, covering in excess of hundreds locations globally. With networks as widespread as such and a multi-modal structure, we have the capability to provide our customers the total logistics solutions. Investing in both bonded and non-bonded warehouses, the logistics hub have enable us to provide one-stop solution to our increasingly growing base of global customers.</p>\r\n",
